      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though a close inspection will reveal some minor surface scratches and a few small stone chips on the hood consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, the car is sound, with all features functioning as intended and a documented service history available for review. It represents a reliable and attractive option for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
