    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior is finished in a stunning coat that retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the trim remains dark and supple. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery maintains its original matte texture and factory-fresh scent, with absolutely no bolster wear or creasing. All technological features, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assists, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is peerless, having been serviced exclusively at scheduled intervals by master technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of inclement weather exposure. Fitted with a brand-new set of matching performance tires on pristine alloy wheels, this vehicle offers a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and indistinguishable from new.",
